Those are exhaust tips for a '74 Z-28.

30
00:04:13,670 --> 00:04:15,547
我專門整理舊車…
I restore old cars, so...

31
00:04:18,341 --> 00:04:20,135
吹風機
Hair-dryer.

32
00:04:29,686 --> 00:04:31,313
我的天，真是抱歉
Oh, my God, I'm so sorry.

33
00:04:34,065 --> 00:04:35,317
撞上癮了
This is getting to be a habit.

34
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:36,443
是啊
Yeah, it is.

35
00:04:38,695 --> 00:04:39,905
很抱歉
Sorry about that.

36
00:04:41,031 --> 00:04:42,574
-謝謝 -沒關係
-Thank you. -Yeah.

37
00:04:44,367 --> 00:04:45,702
-謝謝 -不客氣
-Thank you. -Yeah, sure.

38
00:04:45,869 --> 00:04:46,870
去波士頓？
Boston?

39
00:04:47,412 --> 00:04:48,413
對
Yeah.

40
00:04:49,080 --> 00:04:50,207
12號登機門
Gate 12.

41
00:04:52,167 --> 00:04:53,126
一路順風，賈西亞先生
Enjoy your flight, Mr. Garcia.

42
00:04:53,210 --> 00:04:54,211
謝謝
Thank you.

43
00:04:56,004 --> 00:04:57,923
抱歉，您不在乘客名單上
I'm sorry. You're not on this flight.

44
00:04:58,381 --> 00:05:01,009
我10分鐘前才辦好登記
Well, I just checked in for this one, like, 10 minutes ago.

45
00:05:01,176 --> 00:05:02,427
一定是哪裡出錯了
That must be some sort of mistake.

46
00:05:02,594 --> 00:05:04,721
抱歉，電腦顯示我們客滿了
I'm sorry, the computer shows that we're booked.

47
00:05:04,888 --> 00:05:06,389
聽著，雪莉
Listen, Sharry.

48
