This is the final boarding call for US Midland Air, flight 77

60
00:05:38,547 --> 00:05:40,507
直飛波士頓洛根機場
non-stop service to Boston's Logan Airport, 

61
00:05:40,590 --> 00:05:42,551
請到12號門登機
now boarding at gate 12.

62
00:05:42,717 --> 00:05:45,220
持有效登機證的所有乘客請…
Would all passengers holding a valid boarding pass, please proceed...

63
00:05:45,387 --> 00:05:49,724
我早該料到，他起肖到失控了
I should've seen it coming, boss. He went on tilt, he came undone.

64
00:05:49,891 --> 00:05:52,269
我們這行如果失控大不了喝個幾杯
Coming undone in our business means you need a margarita.

65
00:05:52,435 --> 00:05:54,813
不是在政府實驗室幹掉一票人後
It doesn't mean capping a dozen people in a government lab 

66
00:05:54,896 --> 00:05:55,855
再把它炸掉
and blowing it up.

67
00:05:55,939 --> 00:05:58,275
不是就能竊取重大機密
It doesn't mean stealing an object of critical importance.

68
00:05:58,400 --> 00:05:59,734
他到底有沒有偷走賽佛？
Does he have the Zephyr or not?

69
00:05:59,901 --> 00:06:00,902
我們相信有
We believe so.

70
00:06:02,612 --> 00:06:04,447
你相信有
You believe so.

71
00:06:04,614 --> 00:06:05,574
看一下
Check it out.

72
00:06:05,657 --> 00:06:06,908
我不在乎你相信什麼，費茲
I don't care what you believe, Fitz.

73
00:06:06,992 --> 00:06:08,076
收拾好你的爛攤子
I need you to clean your mess up.

74
00:06:08,159 --> 00:06:09,160
倒帶再放一次
Go back and play it again.

75
00:06:09,244 --> 00:06:10,328
我要拿到賽佛
I want the Zephyr.

76
00:06:10,453 --> 00:06:12,914
我們會在他抵達波士頓時拿到手
We'll have it in hand by the time he lands in Boston.

77
00:06:14,291 --> 00:06:16,126
查出她的身份和背景
Find out who and what she is.

78
00:06:16,293 --> 00:06:18,962
要請威奇塔的分處逮捕她嗎？
Should I have the field office pick her up in Wichita?

79
00:06:20,171 --> 00:06:21,339
我有更好的主意
I got a better idea.

80
00:06:24,342 --> 00:06:25,343
赫文斯小姐
Miss Havens? 

81
00:06:26,303 --> 00:06:27,512
我們替您找到機位了
We did find a seat for you.

82
00:06:29,472 --> 00:06:32,017
請注意，抱歉延誤起飛
I'd like to have your attention, please. We apologize for the delay.

83
00:06:32,183 --> 00:06:34,603
我們很快會從威奇塔機場出發
We will be departing Wichita Airport shortly.

84
00:06:34,769 --> 00:06:35,770
「移動，警告」


85
00:06:35,937 --> 00:06:37,147
感謝您的耐心
Thanks for your patience.

86
00:06:37,772 --> 00:06:40,775
「艾瑪波拉路5826號」


87
00:06:41,318 --> 00:06:43,778
我知道你只是依照公司政策做事
I know it's policy or whatever and it's just your job,

88
00:06:43,945 --> 00:06:45,614
但這實在有點瞎
but it's kind of lame.

89
00:06:45,697 --> 00:06:46,740
真是抱歉
Again, I apologize.

90
00:06:46,823 --> 00:06:49,159
費茲，你動了什麼手腳？
Fitz. What did you do?

91
00:06:52,662 --> 00:06:56,041
難怪航空公司會倒
It's no wonder these airlines are going out of business.

92
00:06:58,209 --> 00:06:59,544
飛機上只有小貓兩三隻
We have been cleared onto the runway. There's nobody on the plane.

93
00:07:08,386 --> 00:07:10,555
機長已開殷系好安全帶指示燈
The captain has turned on the "fasten seatbelt" sign.

94
00:07:10,972 --> 00:07:13,350
請坐在位置上直到指示燈熄滅
Please remain seated until the sign has been turned off

95
00:07:13,516 --> 00:07:15,560
才能在機艙內走動
and it's safe to move about the cabin.

96
00:07:16,353 --> 00:07:18,021
對了，我是茱恩
I'm June, by the way.

97
00:07:18,355 --> 00:07:19,689
我是羅伊米勒
I'm Roy Miller.

98
00:07:19,981 --> 00:07:21,107
幸會
Nice to meet you.

99
00:07:21,191 --> 00:07:22,192
彼此彼此
It's very nice to meet you.

100
00:07:24,027 --> 00:07:25,153
龍舌蘭加冰塊？
Tequila on the rocks?

101
00:07:25,320 --> 00:07:27,030
好，正是時候，謝了
Yeah. Just in time, thanks.

102
00:07:30,909 --> 00:07:33,370
所以你小妹明天結婚？
So, your sister's getting married tomorrow?

103
00:07:34,412 --> 00:07:35,830
-什麼？ -你小妹
-Excuse me? -Your sister.

104
00:07:35,997 --> 00:07:38,500
她明天結婚，恭喜
She's getting married tomorrow. Congratulations.

105
00:07:38,667 --> 00:07:39,918
是啊，謝了
Yeah, thanks.

106
00:07:44,714 --> 00:07:48,176
羅伊，我不善於說謊
You know, Roy, I'm a bad liar.

107
00:07:48,343 --> 00:07:50,095
抱歉，怎麼說？
I'm sorry, how's that?

108
00:07:50,261 --> 00:07:53,181
艾波兒要結婚，不過是週六
April is getting married, but not till Saturday.

109
00:07:53,431 --> 00:07:54,474
你唬到我了
You had me fooled.

110
00:07:54,557 --> 00:07:57,060
可是我明天要試裝
Well, I do have a fitting tomorrow. 

111
00:07:57,227 --> 00:07:59,896
所以我真的得回家
So, I do, actually, have to go home.

112
00:08:07,737 --> 00:08:09,781
希望這趟飛行別太難熬
I hope this isn't gonna be a rough flight.

113
00:08:14,035 --> 00:08:15,412
很難說
It might be.

114
00:08:18,456 --> 00:08:20,875
跑來威奇塔買化油器還真遠
Wichita is a long way to go for a carburetor.

115
00:08:21,042 --> 00:08:22,794
這可不是一般的化油器
It's not just any carburetor. 

116
00:08:22,919 --> 00:08:23,920
是三段式化油器
It's a triple deuce.

117
00:08:24,379 --> 00:08:26,089
我在整理1966年的GTO
I'm restoring a '66 GTO.

118
00:08:26,423 --> 00:08:28,591
堪薩斯州有最棒的零件廠
And Kansas has the best scrap.

119
00:08:28,758 --> 00:08:29,718
真的？
Really?

120
00:08:29,801 --> 00:08:31,386
我爸開修車廠
My dad had a garage,

121
00:08:31,553 --> 00:08:34,264
我小時候，他買了這台車的底盤
and when I was a kid, he bought this chassis.

122
00:08:34,431 --> 00:08:38,435
他經常帶我們到處找零件
He used to take us to yards, and search for parts, you know?

123
00:08:38,810 --> 00:08:42,272
他於1998年過世，如今艾波兒結婚
He died in '98, and now that April's getting married

124
00:08:42,439 --> 00:08:45,442
我心想，何不把車整理好？
I just figured, why not finish it up,

125
00:08:45,608 --> 00:08:47,944
送她當作結婚禮物
give it to her sort of as a wedding present?

126
00:08:48,570 --> 00:08:51,114
也算是老爸送的禮物
Kind of like a present from our dad, too, you know?

127
00:08:52,490 --> 00:08:54,075
好感人
That's nice.

128
00:08:54,242 --> 00:08:55,994
-是啊 -是啊
-Yeah. -Yeah.

129
00:09:05,754 --> 00:09:07,630
我常想
I used to think that

130
00:09:09,799 --> 00:09:13,803
有朝一日，當最後的零件裝上
someday, when the last part went in,

131
00:09:14,763 --> 00:09:17,974
我會爬進那台車，發動它
I would just climb into that GTO and start it up.

132
00:09:19,976 --> 00:09:22,854
一股勁兒地開，不停地開
Just drive and drive and drive, and just keep driving

133
00:09:23,021 --> 00:09:26,316
直到抵達南美洲的盡頭
until I got to the tip of South America.

134
00:09:27,317 --> 00:09:28,318
合恩角
Cape Horn.

135
00:09:29,319 --> 00:09:30,320
對
Yeah.

136
00:09:30,820 --> 00:09:32,655
那裡有美麗的島嶼
There's beautiful islands down there.

137
00:09:32,822 --> 00:09:33,990
是嗎？
Yeah?

138
00:09:34,157 --> 00:09:35,283
海盜島
Pirate islands.

139
00:09:39,788 --> 00:09:42,207
「有朝一日」是個危險字眼
Yeah, "someday." That's a dangerous word.

140
00:09:42,999 --> 00:09:44,000
危險？
Dangerous?

141
00:09:44,834 --> 00:09:48,046
它其實只是「永不」的代名詞
It's really just code for "never."

142
00:09:50,965 --> 00:09:53,468
我常在想我還有什麼事沒做過
I think a lot about things I haven't done.

143
00:09:54,302 --> 00:09:58,348
在大堡礁潛水，乘上東方快車
Dive in the Great Barrier Reef. Ride the Orient Express.

144
00:09:59,140 --> 00:10:00,433
住在阿瑪菲海岸
Live on the Amalfi Coast 

145
00:10:00,517 --> 00:10:03,520
只有摩托車和背包相伴
with nothing but a motorcycle and a backpack.

146
00:10:04,354 --> 00:10:07,524
在海角酒店陽台親吻陌生人
Kiss a stranger on the balcony of the Hotel Du Cap.

147
00:10:10,485 --> 00:10:11,694
那在哪裡？
Where is that?

148
00:10:11,986 --> 00:10:13,655
南法
South of France.

149
00:10:16,866 --> 00:10:18,576
那你呢？
What about you? 

150
00:10:19,369 --> 00:10:20,411
你想做哪些事？
What's your list?

151
00:10:21,871 --> 00:10:25,250
這個嘛…你的聽起來很不賴
Well, yours sounds pretty good.

152
00:10:29,212 --> 00:10:30,505
天啊
Wow.

153
00:10:32,674 --> 00:10:33,675
謝了
Thanks.

154
00:10:34,259 --> 00:10:35,718
別客氣
It's no problem.

155
00:10:37,220 --> 00:10:39,681
不介意的話我放在這裡
I'll just put this up here, if that's all right.

156
00:10:43,935 --> 00:10:45,895
不好意思
You know what?

157
00:10:46,062 --> 00:10:49,190
我要去化妝室整理一下
I'm gonna go back and use the restroom.

158
00:10:50,441 --> 00:10:51,734
我幫你
I'll help you.

159
00:10:51,901 --> 00:10:53,236
謝了
Thanks.

160
00:11:00,118 --> 00:11:01,870
亂流真多
Lots of turbulence, huh?

161
00:11:07,375 --> 00:11:09,878
-我馬上出來 -沒問題
-I'll be out in a minute. -Sure

162
00:11:20,513 --> 00:11:24,017
「在海角酒店陽台親吻陌生人」
"Kiss a stranger on the balcony of the Hotel Du Cap"?

163
00:11:24,100 --> 00:11:25,768
這是什麼台詞？
I mean, what kind of a line is that?

164
00:11:31,733 --> 00:11:35,570
太浪漫了
I mean, it's, like, a really good line.

165
00:11:40,950 --> 00:11:42,452
小姐？小姐？
Ma'am? Ma'am?

166
00:11:51,628 --> 00:11:53,630
你有沒有看見他的手？
Did you see his hands, by any chance?

167
00:11:53,713 --> 00:11:56,424
一下子就接住袋子
They just, like, snatched that bag right out of the air.

168
00:11:56,507 --> 00:11:58,426
超快的反射動作
Lightning-fast reflexes.

169
00:12:01,971 --> 00:12:03,264
太不上道
Not cool.

170
00:12:06,601 --> 00:12:07,894
好
Okay.

171
00:12:28,373 --> 00:12:29,958
這會有幫助
This will help.

172
00:12:45,264 --> 00:12:48,226
夠了，結束了，羅伊
Enough. It's over, Roy.

173
00:12:48,685 --> 00:12:51,187
我同意，夠了
Yeah, I agree. Enough.

174
00:12:51,270 --> 00:12:53,022
賽佛在哪裡？
Where's the Zephyr?

175
00:13:13,042 --> 00:13:16,212
那女的為什麼在機上？快說
Why is the girl on the plane? Tell me.

176
00:13:16,295 --> 00:13:18,089
為什麼費茲安排她上機？
Why did Fitz put her on the plane?

177
00:13:21,050 --> 00:13:22,635
別動，米勒
Don't move, Miller.

178
00:13:34,313 --> 00:13:36,983
好，你打算怎麼做？ 你打算怎麼做？
So what are you gonna do? What are you gonna do?

179
